OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Fsunny spells this evening although
OL,7,Fstaying rather blustery. Remaining
OL,8,Fquite windy overnight in coastal
OL,9,Fregions and over the higher ground. A
OL,10,Fdry night for most but turning
OL,11,Fcloudier with the odd shower moving
OL,12,Finto Cumbria later.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FOften cloudy with a chance
OL,15,Fof occasional showers, these mostly in
OL,16,Fthe north. Sunny intervals are likely
OL,17,Ftoo, these most frequent later in the
OL,18,Fday. Breezy and feeling fairly cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
