OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods on Sunday, but
OL,7,Foccasionally cloudy. Staying mainly
OL,8,Fdry early next week with some strong
OL,9,Fsunshine at times but a chance of a
OL,10,Fshower. Turning much warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
